data.description: Rare Opportunity to get this newly renovated gem, offering a unique opportunity in an unfortunate situation - a short sale. This property has undergone a complete transformation with all new carpet, paint throughout, and new kitchen upgrades. Inside you will find all stainless-steel appliances, washer, dryer, and space to gather. This 3-bedroom 1 bath includes a first-floor space that can be used as an office or the third bedroom. Brand new water heater and recently serviced HVAC system as well. Full basement provides extra storage space and 2-car detached garage is in the rear of the home. Conveniently located just minutes from WPAFB, 5 miles from the University of Dayton, Wright State, and downtown. Great starter home or convenient turnkey rental for your portfolio.
